PyRogue v0.2.0 Summer 2026 By Andrew Butler
Built with Python 3.14

This version of PyRogue is intended to exist as a fully separate Python package; i.e., it does
not include a functional UI component, nor does it run a full game loop on its own.

The idea is to move PyRogue to a state that will enable it to be utilized by any developed frontend.



Notes for myself:
